original_title: 三上悠亜と新ありなと相沢みなみ
overview: The holy grail is here, a very rare and saucy actress crossover.  It’s crazy this movie releases the same day as IPZZ-034. But SSIS-698 is perhaps several times better.  Aizawa Minami is a once-in-a-lifetime actress. I don’t think any other actress tops her beauty, acting, and charisma.  Arata Arina (Hashimoto Arina), who won the best JAV actress award of 2018, successfully relaunched her career by joining MOODYZ; she has instantly become the top actress over there. And I have been loving her recent movies, she’s in fantastic shape.  And Yua Mikami is the main feature of this film. This is, after all, a Yua movie, and since she is retiring, it seems like S1 is on a time race to make up for the lost time.
title: Yua Mikami, Arata Arina And Minami Aizawa
